==Applications==

Products that use ABS
* drain-waste-vent (DWV) pipe systems [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acrylonitrile_butadiene_styrene]
* musical instruments [http://www.absmaterial.com]
* golf club heads [http://www.plasticseurope.org/documents/document/20121120170458-final_plasticsthefacts_nov2012_en_web_resolution.pdf]
* automotive body parts
* protective head gear
* medical devices for blood access
* electronic applications (64% of the total) [https://www.ihs.com/products/acrylonitrile-butadiene-styrene-chemical-economics-handbook.html]
* whitewater canoes
* luggage and protective carrying cases
* small kitchen appliances
* toys
* keyboard keys
* coloring for tattoos
* packaging (barrels, buckets, pallets)

